title: Mazu wa Ubaiai!
sinopse:
What happens when two semes want to take control: Takiyama sensei specialized in surgery, seme number #1 wants nothing more than than to seduce and devour Sakuma sensei specialized in pediatry, but there is only one problem, the latter is also a seme!!!!
The story of a seme vs a seme, and about who is going to be on top.
